T02TD2377E:11a-1: b'a yu tattvam bh'a ba no pa de sha n'a ma /
T02TD2377E:11a-3: rlung gi de nyid bsgom pa'i man ngag ces bya ba /
T02TD2377E:11a-4: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2377E:11a-5: gho ra kha ni ba lang bsrung //
T02TD2377E:11a-6: ba rdzi ba lang 'tsho bar byed //
T02TD2377E:11a-8: nyi ma dang ni zla ba gnyis //
T02TD2377E:11a-10: gho ra kha ni sgra gcan gyis //
T02TD2377E:11a-11: nyi ma zos pa ngo mtshar che //
T02TD2377E:11a-12: gal te rgyab kyi sgal tshigs su //
T02TD2377E:11a-13: drag tu bcings pas rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD2377E:11a-14: skad cig tsam gyis khams su grub //
T02TD2377E:11a-15: gzhom du med cing kun nas dangs //
T02TD2377E:11a-16: stong nyid dngos po rnam par gsal //
T02TD2377E:11a-17: nyi ma dang ni zla ba gnyis //
T02TD2377E:11a-19: gho ra kha ni sgra gcan gyis //
T02TD2377E:11a-20: nyi ma zos pa ngo mtshar che //
T02TD2377E:11a-21: shing bu gter du nub pa dang //
T02TD2377E:11a-23: dga' bas bdag ni bsgrubs so zhes //
T02TD2377E:11a-24: gho ra kha ni smra bar byed //
T02TD2377E:11a-25: nyi ma dang ni zla ba gnyis//
T02TD2377E:11b-1: gho ra kha ni sgra gcan gyis //
T02TD2377E:11b-2: nyi ma zos pa ngo mtshar che //
T02TD2377E:11b-3: nor bu thams cad rdo rjes 'bigs //
T02TD2377E:11b-4: gho ra kha yi rnal 'byor ni //
T02TD2377E:11b-5: bla ma'i drin gyis grub pa yin //
T02TD2377E:11b-6: nyi ma dang ni zla ba gnyis //
T02TD2377E:11b-8: gho ra kha ni sgra gcan gyis //
T02TD2377E:11b-9: nyi ma zos pa ngo mtshar che //
T02TD2377E:11b-10: rlung gi de nyid bsgom pa'i man ngag ces bya ba slob dpon gho ra khas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
